Yeah. Yeah.

730
01:03:59,382 --> 01:04:01,213
You'd think someone...

731
01:04:01,317 --> 01:04:04,150
who designs airplanes
for a living would...

732
01:04:04,254 --> 01:04:06,722
know they need to be grounded.

733
01:04:20,770 --> 01:04:24,672
Fo-- Een-- Phoenix.

734
01:04:24,774 --> 01:04:27,140
You from Phoenix or somethin'?

735
01:04:28,178 --> 01:04:30,339
[ Liddle ]
No. It's not the city.

736
01:04:30,446 --> 01:04:32,641
The phoenix was a desert bird...

737
01:04:32,782 --> 01:04:34,682
from Egyptian mythology.

738
01:04:34,784 --> 01:04:37,275
Consumed itself with fire...

739
01:04:37,420 --> 01:04:39,388
