740
01:04:39,522 --> 01:04:41,752
- Final answer?
- [ Chuckles ]

741
01:04:41,858 --> 01:04:43,553
Final answer.

742
01:04:43,660 --> 01:04:47,187
<i>[ Rady ]</i>
<i>Very good, Mr. Towns. And Mr. Liddle.</i>

743
01:04:47,297 --> 01:04:50,698
