745
01:04:56,072 --> 01:04:58,472
Spirituality is not religion.

746
01:04:58,575 --> 01:05:00,440
Religion divides people.

747
01:05:00,543 --> 01:05:02,511
Belief in something unites them.

748
01:05:06,216 --> 01:05:08,116
