Is that spelled right?

749
01:05:08,218 --> 01:05:11,119
Hey.
[ Chuckles ]

750
01:05:11,221 --> 01:05:14,657
<i>[ Sammi ]</i>
<i>Nah. /t is crooked though.</i>

