817
01:11:29,365 --> 01:11:31,265
Screw this.

818
01:11:31,400 --> 01:11:33,868
[ Continues In Foreign Language ]

819
01:11:35,438 --> 01:11:37,338
Um...

820
01:11:39,075 --> 01:11:41,168
airplane, uh--

821
01:11:41,277 --> 01:11:42,904
Just--Just try ''airplane.''

822
01:11:44,013 --> 01:11:45,776
Airplane.

823
01:11:45,881 --> 01:11:48,475
- [ Grunts ]
- Ah. [ Chuckles ]

824
01:11:49,518 --> 01:11:51,486
[ Shouts In Foreign Language ]

825
01:11:55,925 --> 01:11:58,894
[ Foreign Language ]

826
01:12:01,130 --> 01:12:03,030
What's he saying to me?

827
01:12:03,132 --> 01:12:05,760
I think he's offering to share water.

828
01:12:07,036 --> 01:12:10,972
- [ Foreign Language ]
- [ Repeats Word ]

829
01:12:13,175 --> 01:12:15,336
<i>[ Foreign Language ]</i>

830
01:12:16,545 --> 01:12:19,514
<i>[ /an Speaking Foreign Language ]</i>

831
01:12:21,617 --> 01:12:24,085
- What are you saying?
- They want to know where the plane is.

832
01:12:24,186 --> 01:12:25,915
Don't tell them anything else.

833
01:12:26,022 --> 01:12:27,649
- It's okay.
- Ian--

834
01:12:27,757 --> 01:12:30,590
Do not tell them
where the goddamn plane is.

835
01:12:30,693 --> 01:12:34,094
- [ Foreign Language ]
- [ Foreign Language ]

836
01:12:37,633 --> 01:12:40,625
- What the hell are you doing?
- What's going on?

837
01:12:42,438 --> 01:12:45,498
I'm not sure. Looks okay.

838
01:12:45,641 --> 01:12:48,576
[ Foreign Language ]

839
01:12:49,812 --> 01:12:51,746
- That's my watch!
- Shh.

840
01:12:54,417 --> 01:12:56,510
No!

841
01:13:05,528 --> 01:13:07,996
- Oh, shit.

842
01:13:08,097 --> 01:13:10,190
[ Gunshots ]

843
01:13:11,500 --> 01:13:13,468
Oh, shit!

844
01:13:21,410 --> 01:13:24,311
[ Ian ]
Alex. Alex?

845
01:13:24,413 --> 01:13:26,813
Look at me. Look at me.

846
01:13:26,916 --> 01:13:28,816
Don't die.
Look at me. Look at me.

847
01:13:28,918 --> 01:13:31,318
- Alex.
- Come on, Alex.

848
01:13:31,420 --> 01:13:33,388
Come on, man. Stay with me.

849
01:13:34,690 --> 01:13:36,715
<i>Alex.</i>

850
01:13:38,527 --> 01:13:40,825
-<i>[ Galloping ]</i>
-<i>[ AJ.] Alex, /'m here.</i>

851
01:13:40,930 --> 01:13:42,557
Frank!

852
01:13:42,665 --> 01:13:44,826
<i>[ AJ.]</i>
<i>Come on, man.</i>

853
01:13:46,368 --> 01:13:49,337
<i>Stay with me. Alex.</i>

854
01:13:51,307 --> 01:13:53,673
<i>Alex, look at me. Alex.</i>

855
01:13:55,845 --> 01:13:58,871
[ All Shouting ]

856
01:13:58,981 --> 01:14:01,074
We're almost there!

857
01:14:01,183 --> 01:14:04,414
[ Shouting Continues ]

858
01:14:07,990 --> 01:14:11,050
<i>[ Kelly ]</i>

859
01:14:17,967 --> 01:14:20,162
[ Panting ]

860
01:14:21,670 --> 01:14:24,070
Oh, God!

861
01:14:24,173 --> 01:14:27,301
