We could clean the wound.

864
01:14:33,048 --> 01:14:35,983
- But we'd need water.
- How much water?

865
01:14:36,085 --> 01:14:37,712
As much as he needs!

866
01:14:50,633 --> 01:14:53,761
[ Sobbing ]

867
01:15:04,814 --> 01:15:07,715
<i>[ Liddle ]</i>

868
01:15:10,786 --> 01:15:13,118
