869
01:15:16,559 --> 01:15:18,823
What did he say?

870
01:15:34,310 --> 01:15:37,279
[ Sobbing Continues ]

871
01:16:15,818 --> 01:16:18,787
If I hadn't seen the watch, he--

872
01:16:22,324 --> 01:16:25,225
If you hadn't done what you did...

873
01:16:25,327 --> 01:16:27,295
we'd all be dead.

874
01:16:30,332 --> 01:16:32,323
It's okay.

875
01:16:41,443 --> 01:16:45,038
- You found any water?
- Yep.Just a little bit.

876
01:16:45,147 --> 01:16:47,342
Oh, good.

877
01:16:48,651 --> 01:16:50,676
[ Screams ]

878
01:16:53,055 --> 01:16:55,023
[ Kelly ]
Give us a hand!

879
01:16:56,358 --> 01:16:58,883
Help him! Come on!

880
01:16:58,994 --> 01:17:00,894
Holy shit.

881
01:17:02,131 --> 01:17:04,031
<i>[ Rady ]</i>

882
01:17:04,133 --> 01:17:06,294
