887
01:17:18,480 --> 01:17:20,380
We couldn't just let him die.

888
01:17:20,482 --> 01:17:23,679
And why not?
These bastards killed Rodney.

889
01:17:25,521 --> 01:17:28,422
There's not enough water for anybody else,
and he's not getting any peaches.

890
01:17:28,524 --> 01:17:30,583
Maybe we can give him
some of Rodney's share.

891
01:17:30,693 --> 01:17:33,594
Yeah. Why don't you just offer him
your watch while you at it, asshole?

892
01:17:33,696 --> 01:17:37,029
- He's a human being, man!
- We should have just let them go their own way.

893
01:17:37,132 --> 01:17:39,032
They probably wouldn't even
have seen us.

894
01:17:39,168 --> 01:17:41,932
Don't be stupid. They would have
killed us all if they had a chance.

895
01:17:42,071 --> 01:17:45,700
- You don't know that.
- I know they ain't hesitate
when they killed Rodney!

896
01:17:45,841 --> 01:17:47,741
<i>What are you people thinkin</i>', <i>man?</i>

897
01:17:47,843 --> 01:17:51,472
- He can't stay around here.
- Oh, yeah? Well, where are we gonna take him?

898
01:17:51,580 --> 01:17:54,447
Pick his ass up and drag him back
where you found him at.

899
01:17:54,550 --> 01:17:56,677
- [ Gunshot ]
- Shit!

900
01:18:00,823 --> 01:18:02,916
Well, that settles that.

901
01:18:07,563 --> 01:18:10,464
What the hell is the matter with you?

902
01:18:10,566 --> 01:18:13,501
Oh, shut up.

903
01:18:13,602 --> 01:18:17,834
He would have survived only a couple
of days drinking all of our water.

904
01:18:17,940 --> 01:18:20,602
I did us a favor.

905
01:18:22,444 --> 01:18:25,004
You murdered him, asshole!

906
01:18:26,415 --> 01:18:28,940
No, no, no, no, no, no.

907
01:18:30,619 --> 01:18:34,988
The great Captain Towns
murdered him.

908
01:18:36,859 --> 01:18:38,986
In his infinite wisdom...

909
01:18:39,094 --> 01:18:42,962
he let you go over there,
and I told you not to!

910
01:18:44,166 --> 01:18:46,828
And now we're one man short.

911
01:18:48,404 --> 01:18:51,840
That's 1 2 man-hours lost
every day we work.

912
01:18:51,974 --> 01:18:55,808
Last night alone
cost us 84 man-hours...

913
01:18:55,911 --> 01:18:57,845
because none of you worked at all!

914
01:18:57,946 --> 01:19:00,073
<i>You</i> made the wrong decision!

915
01:19:00,182 --> 01:19:02,650
You could have killed us all again!

916
01:19:02,751 --> 01:19:06,118
You knew we were overweight! I told you
that then, and you just didn't listen!

917
01:19:06,221 --> 01:19:09,748
I had to take on another passenger!
You! Remember?

918
01:19:09,858 --> 01:19:12,656
