953
01:22:15,177 --> 01:22:18,112
Please, can we finish the plane, sir?

954
01:22:18,213 --> 01:22:20,181
Please?

955
01:22:20,282 --> 01:22:22,443
Ian.

956
01:22:23,485 --> 01:22:26,682
